---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Sonvice Group" description="Our privacy policy explains how we handle your personal data in accordance with GDPR regulations.">
<main class="relative overflow-hidden">
	<!-- Hero/Title section -->
	<section class="relative bg-white pt-24 pb-12 bg-grid-pattern border-b border-slate-100">
		<div class="absolute top-[20%] left-[10%] w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-glow-teal rounded-full blur-[80px] -z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 reveal-on-scroll">
			<span class="text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-widest">Legal Document</span>
			<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text-heading mt-2">
				Privacy Policy
			</h1>
			<p class="text-slate-600 text-xs mt-2">Last updated: June 3, 2026</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Content section -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white relative">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 reveal-on-scroll">
			<div class="prose max-w-none text-text-body space-y-8">
				<div class="space-y-3">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-heading">1. Introduction</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
						Sonvice Group AB values your personal privacy and strives to protect your personal data in the best possible way. This policy describes how we collect, use, transfer, and store your data in accordance with current legislation, including the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-heading">2. Personal Data We Collect</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
						We collect data that you provide to us when you request a quote, book a service, or contact us. This may include:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm space-y-1.5">
						<li>Name and contact details (email, phone number, address)</li>
						<li>Information about your residence or roof for pricing estimation</li>
						<li>Personal identity number (required for RUT or ROT tax credit applications)</li>
						<li>IP address and browsing behavior when visiting our website (via cookies)</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-heading">3. Purposes and Legal Basis</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
						We process your data for the following purposes:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm space-y-1.5">
						<li>To fulfill our agreements with you (e.g., executing moving or cleaning services).</li>
						<li>To manage tax deductions like RUT and ROT with the Swedish Tax Agency (Skatteverket).</li>
						<li>To answer your requests and send quotes based on our legitimate interest.</li>
						<li>To optimize our website and marketing based on your consent (cookies).</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-heading">4. Data Retention</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
						We do not store your personal data longer than necessary for the respective purpose. For example, contract and billing data is saved for seven years in accordance with the Swedish Accounting Act (Bokföringslag). Quote requests that do not lead to a contract are normally deleted within 12 months.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-heading">5. Your Rights</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
						You have the right to request a free extract of the personal data we process about you. You also have the right to request correction, deletion ("the right to be forgotten"), or restriction of the processing of your data. Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@sonvicegroup.se" class="text-accent underline font-semibold">info@sonvicegroup.se</a> for such requests.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-heading">6. Contact Information</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
						The data controller for the processing of your personal data is:
					</p>
					<address class="not-italic text-sm bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200/60 p-5 rounded-xl space-y-1 text-slate-700">
						<strong>Sonvice Group AB</strong><br />
						Kronoberg/Kalmar, Sweden<br />
						Email: <a href="mailto:info@sonvicegroup.se" class="text-accent underline font-semibold">info@sonvicegroup.se</a><br />
						Phone: 08-123 45 67
					</address>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>
</Layout>
